channel.title: Drum Machine Videos --- Spot the Axoloti!
channel.description:
I started working on my Axoloti Drum Machine again after almost 2 years.
Here are some unexplained videos for you. Posting helps motivate me to finish-up a few things (better bass drum sound, BCR patch save recall, create eurorack power converter mini board, etc).
Spot the Axoliti!
Ask questions!
